&lt;h4&gt;3. Load user settings from &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/drog/config/tree/master/home/diego/.config/sublime-text-3/Packages/User/Preferences.sublime-settings&quot;&gt;Sublime Text 3 config&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;PostgreSQL config&lt;/h3&gt;
