&lt;h2&gt;Power managment&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot; data-lang=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;pacman -S  tlp lm_sensors smartmontools lsb-release ethtool iw
